====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary}} long-tailed [[monkey]] (similar to a [[macaque]] but larger)
#* {{zh-x|爰 有 熊、羆、文虎、蜼{wèi}、豹、離朱、視肉。|There are the bear, the brown bear, the tiger, the '''long-tailed monkey''', the leopard, the ''lizhu'' and the ''shirou''.|ref=Shanhaijing}}
#* {{zh-x|猨{yuán} 蜼{wèi} 晝 吟，鼯鼠 夜 叫。|The ape and '''long-tailed monkey''' sing in the day; the flying squirrel calls at night.|CL|ref={{lw|zh|馬融 (東漢)|馬融}} ({{w|Ma Rong}}), {{lang|zh|長笛賦}} (“Rhapsody on Long Flute”), in {{lw|zh|文選}} (''{{w|Selections of Refined Literature}}'')}}
#* {{zh-x|於是乎 玄猨{yuán} 素 雌，蜼{wèi} 玃{jué} 飛𧕫{lěi}，蛭 蜩 蠼猱，獑{chán}胡 豰{hù} 蛫{guǐ}，棲息 乎 其間。||CL|ref={{lw|zh|司馬相如}} ({{w|Sima Xiangru}}), {{lang|zh|上林賦}} (“''Fu'' on the Shanglin Park”), in {{lw|zh|文選}} (''{{w|Selections of Refined Literature}}'')}}
#* {{zh-x|不 辨 過 河 牛，時 看 掛 樹 蜼。|Not recognizing the cattle that are crossing the river, always seeing the '''monkeys''' that are hanging in the trees.|CL|ref={{lw|zh|吳寬}}, {{lang|zh|次韻啟南淫雨}}}}

